 I Haraldsson - Earl of Orkney(은)는 17세였고, 그녀의 어머니 Aufrica Duncandaughter of Methil Fife Maddad Earl of Caithness and Orkney(은)는 40세였다. 그녀는 대략 1200년 Hugh Freskin de Moravia Lord of Duffus and Sutherland(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 두 명의 아들과 한 명의 딸을 두었다. 그녀는 1268년 스컷랜드 엘긴실르 더프스에서 93세의 나이로 사망했으며 스컷랜드 엘긴실르에 묻혔다."},"lv":{"1175–1268":"1175.gads–1268.gads","1160–1220":"1160–1220","1190–1248":"1190–1248.gads","1205–1263":"1205–1263.gads","1223–Female":"1223–mirusi","1158–1231":"1158–1231.gads","1135–1160":"1135–1160","1190":"1190","Abt 1205":"ap 1205. gadu","1231":"1231. gads","1220":"1220","1175":"1175. gads","1263":"1263. gads","1160":"1160","1205":"1205","1248":"1248. gads","1269":"1269. gads","1268":"1268. gads","1158":"1158","Abt 1200":"ap 1200. gadu","1135":"1135","1223":"1223","Abt 1220":"ap 1220. gadu","about 1223":"ap 1223. gadu","Abt 1190":"ap 1190. gadu","Dunrobin Castle, Golspie, Moray, Perthshire, Scotland":"Golspie, Highland, Skotija, Lielbritānija","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Skotija, Lielbritānija","Duffus, Moray, Scotland":"Duffus, Moray, Skotija, Lielbritānija","Morayshire, Scotland":"Elginshire, Scotland","Thurso, Caithness, Scotland":"Thurso, Caithness, Skotija, Lielbritānija","Duffus, Morayshire, Scotland":"Duffus, Elginshire, Scotland"},"mg":{"1175–1268":"1175–1268","1160–1220":"1160–1220","1190–1248":"1190–1248","1205–1263":"1205–1263","1223–Female":"1223–Maty","1158–1231":"1158–1231","1135–1160":"1135–1160","1190":"1190","Abt 1205":"tany ho any amin'ny 1205","1231":"1231","1220":"1220","1175":"1175","1263":"1263","1160":"1160","1205":"1205","1248":"1248","1269":"1269","1268":"1268","1158":"1158","Abt 1200":"tany ho any amin'ny 1200","1135":"1135","1223":"1223","Abt 1220":"tany ho any amin'ny 1220","about 1223":"tany ho any amin'ny 1223","Abt 1190":"tany ho any amin'ny 1190","Dunrobin Castle, Golspie, Moray, Perthshire, Scotland":"Golspie, Highland, Écosse, United Kingdom","Scotland, United Kingdom":"Écosse, United Kingdom","Duffus, Moray, Scotland":"Duffus, Mor